    "notes": "Round 20 repair attempt from the C08 scope-overlap line. Intended proof: a small entry count confirms A1, the overlap rule then saturates B1/A2 as safe and reveals B1 as a bottle, the bottle chain reveals B2 as a bottle, and B2 finally confirms C2. This explicitly tests whether a derived guest can feed scopeOverlapCount across proof waves without reducing the overlap rule itself to an opening-observation giveaway."
